name: FeedFido
0:
”Alexa, tell Feed Fido I fed Fluffy”
”Alexa, ask Feed Fido when did Fluffy eat”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: feed fido
des: You can tell feed fido when you feed your dog. Later when you ask feed fido when you last fed the dog, it will tell you how much time has past since you logged a feeding. Feed fido can also be used between family members, that way you wont accidentally feed your dog twice OR even worse forget to feed them at all.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
